/dc-testament/dc/59.html?verse=13-15#p13" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/59.13-15?lang=eng#p13">Doctrine and Covenants 59:13–15</a>.</p></li><li data-marker=13. id=note13><p data-aid=139950217 id=note13_p1><cite><a class=cross-ref data-old-href="../../../manual/handbook-2-administering-the-church/leadership-in-the-church-of-jesus-christ.html?para=title_number19#title_number19" href="/manual/handbook-2-administering-the-church/leadership-in-the-church-of-jesus-christ?lang=eng&para=title_number19#title_number19">Handbook 2: Administering the Church</a></cite> (2010), 3.4.</p></li></ol></footer></div></article><div class=startHandle-2o_6p touch-action=none></div><div class=endHandle-wg4Dv touch-action=none></div></div><div class="callout-EaEKb hidden-6EhVw sc-bZQynM dDOxTx" style=bottom:NaNpx><div class="sc-htoDjs fHktW"><div class="sc-gzVnrw kPxdrJ"></div><div class=signIn-215_y></div><div class=annotationMenu-YPu2S><div class=menuItem-39B5x disabled=""><button class=iconButton--V5Iv><svg style=width:1.5rem;height:1.5rem viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg role=presentation> <path fill=currentColor d="M10.468 15.92l-3.434.606-1.117 1.117a1.403 1.403 0 0 1-.86.357H2.323c-.555 0-.687-.319-.295-.71l2.884-2.885.606-3.434 7.264-7.264c.39-.39 1.158-.707 1.71-.707h7.893c.554 0 .684.32.29.713L10.468 15.92zm0 0l1.06-1.06L6.58 9.91l-1.06 1.06 4.95 4.95zM1.752 19.5a.75.75 0 1 0 0 1.5h15.496a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5H1.752z"> </path></svg></button><span class=menuItemLabel-3XB1V>Mark</span></div><div class=menuItem-39B5x disabled=""><button class=iconButton--V5Iv><svg style=width:1.5rem;height:1.5rem viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg role=presentation> <path fill=currentColor d="M18.55 11.54a.75.75 0 1 1 1.5 0v9.76a1.75 1.75 0 0 1-1.75 1.75H2.75A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 1 21.3V5.75C1 4.784 1.783 4 2.75 4H12a.75.75 0 1 1 0 1.5H2.75a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25V21.3c0 .138.112.25.25.25H18.3a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-9.76zm3.96-8.325c.685.684.682 1.794-.005 2.48l-1.232 1.2